### Component 6: Validation Service (NEW)

#### [NEW] [reconciliationValidationService.js](file:///d:/SBG/ilabs1/src/engine/reconciliationValidationService.js)

Hidden validation logic for manual matching:

- `validateMatch(ledgerItemId, statementItemId)` → returns `{ valid: boolean }`
- Validation rules (hidden from user):
  - Both items must be `Outstanding`
  - One must be `LEDGER`, other must be `STATEMENT`
  - `amount` must match (penny tolerance)
  - `currency` must match
  - `valueDate` must match (date-only comparison)
  - Internal cross-reference check via configured fields
- User never sees WHY a match failed — only "Match successful" or "Items cannot be matched"
- Uses `ReconciliationConfig` for configurable field matching

