## Performance Considerations

- ReconciliationRepository uses existing compound indexes (`status+source`, `status+reconDesk`, `itemRef1`)
- Allocation queries use indexed `currentStatus: "SETTLED"` field
- Batch operations for auto-trade generation use `insertMany` with `ordered: false`
- All fire-and-forget patterns preserved (ledger/statement creation never blocks trade lifecycle)

