## Future Scalability

The ReconciliationRepository abstraction enables:
- Partial matching (match score < 100%)
- One-to-many matching (1 ledger ↔ N statements)
- Duplicate statement detection
- Suspense items
- Reconciliation profiles (cash, securities, nostro, FX)
- Auto-match rules engine
- TLM-style matching workflows
- Reconciliation ageing and SLA tracking
